properties.name: memcached.cache.expiration
properties.description: Cache expiration in seconds. The default is 60 seconds.

properties.name: memcached.cache.host
properties.description: Memcached server host. The default is 'localhost'.

properties.name: memcached.cache.mode
properties.description: Memcached client mode. The default mode is 'static'. Use 'dynamic' mode for AWS node auto discovery.

properties.name: memcached.cache.namespace
properties.description: Namespace key value used for invalidation of cached values. The default value is 'namespace'.

properties.name: memcached.cache.port
properties.description: Memcached server port. The default is 11211.

properties.name: memcached.cache.prefix
properties.description: Cached object key prefix. The default is 'memcached:spring-boot'.

properties.name: memcached.cache.servers
properties.description: Memcached server list. The default is 'localhost:11211'.
